medplum/medplum#7428.body:
When searching for many resources via GraphQL Connection API, there should be `next`, `last`, `first`, `previous`, etc links in the `Connection` object.

Those links are currently missing.

Spec: https://hl7.org/fhir/R4/graphql.html#searching

Implementation: https://github.com/medplum/medplum/blob/main/packages/fhir-router/src/graphql/graphql.ts#L309-L346

Note that we're not setting `next`.

The good news is that the `Bundle` already has all of the necessary details:

```json
    "link": [
        {
            "relation": "self",
